---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import DefaultCTA from "../components/cta/DefaultCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Our Approach - ROM Business Psychology">

<!-- BREADCRUMB -->
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    <nav class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-cyan-600">Home</a>
      <svg class="w-4 h-4 mx-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="text-gray-900">About</span>
    </nav>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE CHALLENGE - HERO WITH IMAGE -->
<section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <img 
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551818255-e6e10975bc17?w=1920&h=1080&fit=crop&q=80" 
    alt="Hectic business reality"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl py-20">
      <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 font-semibold">
        The challenge
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-white">
        It's an Hectic Reality<br/>Out There
      </h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CHALLENGE DESCRIPTION -->
<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      The challenges that business leaders face today are enormous. New technologies outpace our ability to grasp them, competition is more aggressive and the regulatory environment can be restrictive. On top of all that, individuals are more sophisticated than they ever were. Nevertheless, precious opportunities await us to proactively manage this complexity.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TAGLINE -->
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
    <h2 class="text-gray-900 leading-tight">
      Translating the Human Operating System into leadership principles
    </h2>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE APPROACH -->
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-cyan-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The approach
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Working with the HOS<br/>(Human Operating System)
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center mb-12">
      
      <!-- Left - Image -->
      <div class="relative h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559136555-9303baea8ebd?w=800&h=800&fit=crop&q=80" 
          alt="Human Operating System"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right - Content -->
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Although the world has changed immensely, the "HOS" has remained relatively the same.
        </p>
        <p class="italic text-gray-600">
          And no, there are no updates to downloadâ€¦
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Our approach is to explore and articulate generic human principles and learn about their interaction with organizational cultures and dynamics. We then develop managerial solutions and train leaders with these solutions. Using resilient work methodologies, leaders learn ways to increase their managerial and team capacity.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- TAGLINE 2 -->
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
    <h2 class="text-gray-900 leading-tight">
      Assembling practical solutions in order to broaden our behavioral repertoire
    </h2>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE SOLUTION -->
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-cyan-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Solution
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Simple, Brave, Eye-Leveled
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We rather learn from experience. All our practitioners hold profound managerial experience. They know what it's like out there.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-cyan-50 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-8 my-8">
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Initially, our consultants analyze the organizational situation and map the challenges. Subsequently, they are able to offer simple solutions for a wide range of personal and organizational phenomena.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
        Because everybody is special, we offer tailor-made solutions
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- WIDE SPECTRUM -->
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-cyan-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        Wide Spectrum
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Counseling & Training Solutions
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center mb-8">
      
      <!-- Left - Content -->
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          We offer a wide spectrum of counseling and training solutions; starting from planning career and developmental path, through increasing personal effectiveness, motivating team and advancing it's efficiency.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right - Parachute Image -->
      <div class="relative h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1478860409698-8707f313ee8b?w=800&h=800&fit=crop&q=80" 
          alt="Parachute - safety and support"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>

    </div>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      And ending with acquiring mentoring and leadership behaviors, enhancing influential capabilities and maximizing collaboration. In order to achieve these goals and many more, managers should follow certain mental, emotional and behavioral principles that can be taught and internalized.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>


<Footer />

</Layout>